{"tid":136201,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【脫歐後遺】蘇格蘭傳公投獨立！ 英鎊兩日跌1.3%","createTime":"2017-02-27T01:36:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-27T01:37:42.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"08154b1a96ba2cfc25452a5ff199e03e49668711","tid":136201,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T01:36:35.000Z","msg":"2017-02-27 08:21:12 HKT  <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n英國脫歐程序下月啟動，英國傳媒報導，蘇格蘭有意下月宣布進行獨立公投，預告明年舉行「脫英」公投，並有信心可以正式獨立，有傳英國首相文翠珊團隊正努力準備，有機會同意蘇格蘭舉行公投，英鎊繼上星期五一度下跌1%，今早曾繼續腳軟跌多0.5%。<br />\n<br />\n蘇格蘭再傳獨立，反映脫歐不受歡迎，英鎊再次下挫，兌美元上周五一度跌1%，至1.2428，跌0.8%，報1.2455；今早一度跌0.5%，報1.2392，最新跌0.3%，報1.2422。英鎊兌港元由上周五9.74跌至今早最弱見過9.6171，兩日累跌1.3%，最新報9.6405，跌0.32%。<br />\n<br />\n蘇格蘭2014年已經試過獨立公投，不過以10個百分點落敗，未能脫英。英國去年6月脫歐公投，投票結果顯示，蘇格蘭人支持英國留歐，可惜最後不敵脫歐人數而被迫跟隨脫歐，其後，蘇格蘭多次提出脫英獨立。<br />\n<br />\n掌握財經生活資訊，即Like「蘋果ATM」fb專頁啦！<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/appledailyatm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fappledailyatm&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07DwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=21d819b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/appledailyatm</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56358762&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170227\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56358762%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170227&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07DwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=dc761ecd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56358762%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170227&h=62a02583\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56358762&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170227</a>"},{"pid":"b536c671996dd5e30c82d998d72009a693a5fe99","tid":136201,"uid":11895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T01:37:42.000Z","msg":"又投<br />\n投到贏為止?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}